  "body": "We want to move to RESTEasy Reactive by default. It is also a good opportunity to adjust the default behavior.\r\n\r\nI think we should change the behavior to:\r\n- do not add RESTEasy Reactive automatically if at least one extension is specified: Quarkus is used for a lot of things now and forcing a REST impl by default when other extensions are specified makes little sense\r\n- add RESTEasy Reactive by default if no extensions have been added",
